# UI style guide + themeable styling (notion_pipeliner_ui)

Canonical rule: **`notion_pipeliner_ui/.cursor/rules/ui-style-guide-first.mdc`**.

**Summary:** `styleguide/` defines how the app should look for developers. In code, reference **global CSS variables and shared classes** (`index.css`, `App.css`, runtime theme on `.app-shell`) so **admin and runtime theme changes propagate**—avoid hardcoding theme-sensitive colors or surfaces in components.
